========================================================
ACCURACY RULES
========================================================

- Do not assume endpoints.
- Only record findings supported by source code or configuration.
- If uncertain, mark as:
  - Potential Endpoint
  - Requires Manual Validation
- Avoid duplicate entries.
- Normalize endpoint paths.
- Preserve exact source paths.
- Include overloaded mappings separately.

========================================================
RECURSIVE DEPENDENCY ANALYSIS
========================================================

Where possible, trace:

- controller → service → repository
- servlet → handler → backend service
- route → middleware → downstream API

Document observable usage behavior.

========================================================
PERFORMANCE EXPECTATIONS
========================================================

- Handle very large repositories.
- Continue scanning even if parsing errors occur.
- Log skipped or unreadable files.
- Avoid terminating on malformed code.

